dataset_id: Aboveground Biomass, Landcover, and Degradation, Kalimantan Forests, Indonesia, 2014
title: Aboveground Biomass, Landcover, and Degradation, Kalimantan Forests, Indonesia, 2014
summary: This dataset provides estimates of aboveground biomass, percent canopy cover, mean canopy height, landcover, and forest degradation index products for forests in Kalimantan, Indonesia (Island of Borneo) representative of conditions in late 2014. Data were combined from several sources including field sampling, airborne lidar, satellite measurements, a forest-type land cover map, and integrated into a random forest algorithm to produce these estimates.
